{"tid":1614630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大叫「天滅中共  全黨死清光」「驅逐共黨  光復香港」就叫對了口號","createTime":"2019-10-03T00:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T05:13:15.000Z","uid":131157,"like":57,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"06bc263d4914010a459ae44f6d767bb3c7207b16","tid":1614630,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:22:34.000Z","msg":"要改口叫「天滅中共  全黨死清光」「驅逐共黨  光復香港」<br />\n<br />\n政治是推廣理念，推廣理念由叫口號開始。「時代革命」口號叫錯了，就是政治錯誤，政治錯誤的後果非常嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n據說「時代革命」是「世代革命」的委婉辭。我認為此口號根本是不知所謂，白白浪費口水和精力，不單放過了鬥爭的對象，還打草驚蛇。口號不知所謂，鬥爭對象只知你要對付自己，卻不知道「時代革命」只不過是鼓勵世代交替。故此，不能作出合理回應，只能不知所謂地收拾你。<br />\n<br />\n「時代革命」簡直是垃圾口號，直接叫「廢老納命來」還更好。老老實實要對方的命，反而對方知道如何作合理反應。再者光復香港的鬥爭對象並非「廢老」，而是共產黨，叫「時代革命」是雙重政治錯誤，豈能不敗？<br />\n<br />\n要勝利要認清楚鬥爭對象，並且老老實實喊出鬥爭目標。大叫「天滅中共  全黨死清光」「驅逐共黨  光復香港」就叫對了口號，口號對了政治就正確，政治正確就會贏。<br />\n<br />\n簡單到難以置信，當然蠢人總喜歡複雜地輸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=931610977204609&amp;id=100010671456369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D931610977204609%26id%3D100010671456369&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7FT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=6a0437b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=931610977204609&amp;id=100010671456369</a>"},{"pid":"afe0d8c13306607ee3e56a9ee3ff91843091c0d5","tid":1614630,"uid":177089,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"其實佢知唔知時代革命點解"},{"pid":"3453c0190e6a72fe255216eb30d37ba413257d35","tid":1614630,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8b74b5566493986724eba76ecf6903cceaf694","tid":1614630,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"afe0d8c13306607ee3e56a9ee3ff91843091c0d5","tid":1614630,"uid":177089,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"其實佢知唔知時代革命點解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:25:07.000Z","msg":"以後出黎加埋呢個口號得唔得先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cc1b057b97aaf99030144611287a526a89a9a0","tid":1614630,"uid":27647,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"afe0d8c13306607ee3e56a9ee3ff91843091c0d5","tid":1614630,"uid":177089,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"其實佢知唔知時代革命點解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:27:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陳雲</span></strong>：<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">正確口號，威力最大。叫喊</span><span style=\"color: red;\">「驅逐共黨，光復香港」、「天滅中共，全黨死清光」</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">之後，香港已經有一個共產黨死了，另一個就來死。這就是正確革命口號的威力。再叫下去，江澤民、習近平都會死去。<br />\n這個革命口號，向住衙差、共匪黑幫叫喊，威力更加大，他們聽了一定心虛腳軟，掉頭走，因為繼續站著對抗，就是自認共產黨。</span>"},{"pid":"9b6d6a0048cf02e0d0a9f4f3239eb66040aff8c1","tid":1614630,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21c138d154257c7449a5274ab329fedfa08230d","tid":1614630,"uid":3662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:37:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"926bfc3697d5f87b2140f2da2d6869aaa896ad48","tid":1614630,"uid":210612,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:38:37.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好撞光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b38e7c7de065ca991905a916a1bfb5b2341c52","tid":1614630,"uid":64469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:41:40.000Z","msg":"［我有野講］咪撚再唱歌叫口號［入黎睇下自己衰咩］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612280</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d9dc8c3e539a842fce02f0db955864f405c86aa","tid":1614630,"uid":3662,