da2d6869aaa896ad48","tid":1614630,"uid":210612,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:38:37.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好撞光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n<br />\n叫啱口號重要，但有樣嘢忽略咗<br />\n<br />\n你隔硬借「光復香港」一句去加上自己的口號有啲怪，句「時代革命」好地地叫咗咁耐又集到氣，無啦啦轉一句啲人叫出黎都覺得怪<br />\n仲未計你（或者陳雲）果句「驅逐共黨」冇咗個產字，叫都叫得唔順口。<br />\n一句口號唔順口，好難叫得出口。<br />\n<br />\n如果你識得講政治係要令人認同自己，我建議陳雲一派的人好好認真思考，點樣可以落地啲，諗吓說服技巧，齋屌人唔聽話就輸係冇用架，咁同屌票有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n陳雲有理論，但啲追隨者質素參差，上上下下成派人成日用說教口吻去發表意見。雖忠言逆耳，但聽唔入耳講咩都冇用。要人虛心受教，你都唔好自視過高。<br />\n<br />\n不過出聲屌泛民應該冇乜人反對，揀啱時間屌效果更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9d2e97c43c22c6761e4f6c0eaf4bd8ee120bb6","tid":1614630,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18067af83582aabe94af669c06e8f5eb28d69546","tid":1614630,"uid":195270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"時代革命點解唔重要，重點係革命呢兩個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea742e2965dd3a2ce80b4efa707d5ab2ba25472","tid":1614630,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01fee4a0f14d0d95ebea5a287ec01399a730be9"